      <p class="p2">
      Indus Global Academy of Technical Education welcomes each one of you to our CAMPUS where latest technology, innovative teaching methodologies and quality education are blended together with industrial exposure to create a complete engineer. We build solid engineers, whether it may be a student from Diploma students from Technical Board of Education, Students from Bachelor of Engineering (BE) or Masters in Engineering (ME / MTech) Colleges and Universities. We have courses well defined for each category of students depending upon their career goals. You are most welcome to browse through our web site and contact us for more information.
